Check out my dear friend @chanelledelau children’s book on Amazon Kindle, titled: “Pia The Poodle - The journey to loving myself.” 
The purpose of her book is to uplift, inspire and teach youngsters valuable soul’s journey lessons. For Pia the Poodle 🐩, this is all about Self Love and embracing what makes her unique!

Perfect for children aged 3-11. 📖
